enhanced_by.reason: normalizeAttributes method prepares the Attributes object which may contain the attribute names to be normalized by normalizeAttribute.
The preserveAttributeCase method determines whether the attribute name should be normalized, which is directly used in the normalizeAttribute method.
Both normalizeTag and normalizeAttribute methods perform similar normalization operations based on case preservation settings.
The normalName method also performs a similar normalization operation by trimming and lower-casing the input string, which can be used to construct assertions for normalizeAttribute.
